| type = Album notes
| publisher = [[Flashback Records (Bell)|Sphere Sound Records]]
| id = SSR 7002
| OCLC = 
| location = Label
| ref = harv
}}</ref>  Both the 1954 and 1960–1961 versions appear on numerous later James compilations.<ref>
{{cite web
